      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>When worn, this mask transforms the wearer's face into a stone statue and its voice into an emotionless monotone. Though it allows the wearer to speak, its facial expressions and voice betray little emotion, granting a +10 competence bonus on Bluff checks made to lie and a +5 competence bonus on Bluff checks made to feint, but also imposing a -5 penalty on Bluff checks made to pass a hidden message.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, innocence (Advanced Player's Guide), stone shape</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Ultimate Equipment",
